2024
We understand that the data you send to Realytics is confidential and treat it as such. We will never share the data you send us with anyone unless required by law. Access will be restricted to the team members you invite, and to certain Realytics staff in order to provide support and develop the service.
We do reserve the right to publish aggregated studies, scrubbed of any identifying information, in order to advance the web analytics field and to help promote Realytics.
Who we are
Realytics SAS with registered office address at  89, boulevard Pereire, 75017, Paris, France is a global platform for data-driven media buying, audience measurement and media performance analysis.
You can contact us at any time if you have any questions or comments regarding this Privacy policy using
privacy@realytics.io
.
This Privacy Policy describes how we collects and uses data from web sites, applications and other digital properties in connection with our products and services as well as from our corporate web sites :
https://www.realytics.io
https://www.adkymia.com
and how individuals can manage choices and exercise rights related to certain data collected or used in our products, services and Realytics owned web sites.
It also explains your rights in relation to your personal data and how to contact us or authorities in the event you have a complaint.
We are responsible as ‘controllers’  of the personal data we collect and use it regarding the
General Data Protection Regulation
, which applies across the European Union.
What are our services
Realytics build smart technologies that deliver a relevant and efficient advertising experience for consumer and brands.  We make television editors spaces which deliver premium advertising available to all brands in simple and efficient manner.
Realytics does not provide services directly to consumers but provide our business client with services.
AdPerformance measures the performance of advertiser TV campaign using audience analytics advanced capabilities
Adkymia allow brands to add TV in their video buying capabilities
To achieve these goals for our customer we may collect informations regarding individuals.
The personal information that you may be asked to provide, and the reasons why you are asked to provide it, will be made clear to you at the point we ask you to provide your personal information.
