What data do we collect
A cookie is a small amount of data that is sent to your browser from our servers and stored on your computer’s hard drive.
We generally use cookies to access information when you sign in, to store your preferences, to keep you logged in, and to store a limited amount of behavioral data.
Corporate Websites
